<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 21:09:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国副气候特使表示，中美两国正在推进遏制甲烷排放的工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/us-china-advance-work-curbing-methane-emissions-us-deputy-climate-envoy-says-2024-03-19/</link><description>美国气候变化问题副特使周二表示，中美在甲烷方面的合作正在推进，北京有机会以很少或没有成本的方式削减其庞大煤炭行业的排放量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/us-china-advance-work-curbing-methane-emissions-us-deputy-climate-envoy-says-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>汽车老板德梅奥呼吁欧洲采取联合措施对抗中国电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/car-boss-de-meo-calls-joint-european-approach-counter-chinese-evs-2024-03-19/</link><description>雷诺首席执行官兼欧洲汽车制造商协会（ACEA）主席卢卡·德梅奥周二向欧洲政策制定者发出公开信，呼吁加强合作以与中国电动汽车制造商竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 15:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/car-boss-de-meo-calls-joint-european-approach-counter-chinese-evs-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>卫冕冠军意大利将在戴维斯杯中迎战比利时、巴西和荷兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/holders-italy-face-belgium-brazil-netherlands-davis-cup-2024-03-19/</link><description>冠军意大利队将在九月份的戴维斯杯决赛小组赛中迎战比利时、巴西和荷兰。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 15:30:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/holders-italy-face-belgium-brazil-netherlands-davis-cup-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>法拉利因刹车缺陷被美国车手起诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ferrari-is-sued-by-us-drivers-over-brake-defect-2024-03-19/</link><description>法拉利在美国被司机起诉，称这家意大利豪华跑车制造商未能修复可能部分或全部丧失制动能力的车辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 14:07:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ferrari-is-sued-by-us-drivers-over-brake-defect-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>首席财务官悲观前景导致西门子股价跌至一年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/siemenss-share-slump-one-year-low-after-cfos-gloomy-outlook-2024-03-19/</link><description>西门子首席财务官拉尔夫·托马斯在周二的美国银行会议上表示，其旗舰数字产业部门第二季度的收入将持平，随后该公司股价跌至一年来的最低点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 13:35:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/siemenss-share-slump-one-year-low-after-cfos-gloomy-outlook-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>第23条：香港新国安法你需要了解的事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/article-23-what-you-need-know-about-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-19/</link><description>尽管西方政府担心香港这个金融中心的自由会受到进一步破坏，但香港90个席位的立法机关周二一致通过了一项新的国家安全法，该法在提出后仅11天。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 13:17:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/article-23-what-you-need-know-about-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港新国安法的范围有哪些？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/scope-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-19/</link><description>香港周二通过了新的国家安全法，该法案扩大了破坏、煽动叛乱和国家机密等犯罪的定义，并规定了最严厉的处罚，最高可达终身监禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 13:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/scope-hong-kongs-new-national-security-laws-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港通过国安法，批评者称这进一步威胁自由</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-unanimously-passes-new-national-security-law-2024-03-19/</link><description>香港立法会议员周二在提出后两周内一致通过了一项新的国家安全法案，快速推进了一项重要立法，批评者称该法案进一步威胁了这座中国统治城市的自由。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 11:05:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-unanimously-passes-new-national-security-law-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国蚂蚁集团任命新总裁，这是监管改革以来最大规模的人事变动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-ant-group-appoints-new-president-biggest-reshuffle-since-regulatory-2024-03-19/</link><description>据一位周二看到蚂蚁集团首席执行官兼董事长井贤栋内部电子邮件的消息人士透露，韩信谊将成为中国蚂蚁集团总裁，该金融科技公司的一些部门将成立自己的董事会，以更加独立地运营。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-ant-group-appoints-new-president-biggest-reshuffle-since-regulatory-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>香港立法会三读通过国安法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-passes-third-reading-national-security-bill-2024-03-19/</link><description>香港立法会议员周二通过了新的国家安全法案三读，距离全面通过又近了一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-legislature-passes-third-reading-national-security-bill-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本从颠倒的世界中回归，人工智能开始发力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-19/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国小鹏汽车预计 2023 年结束后电动汽车交付量将增加，亏损将减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-forecast-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-03-19/</link><description>电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车公布的季度亏损小于预期，并预计 1 月至 3 月期间的交付量将增加，这为担心中国汽车市场价格战造成影响的投资者提供了一些喘息的机会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-forecast-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>随着世界杯预赛的恢复，亚洲冠军卡塔尔队转移焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-champions-qatar-shift-focus-world-cup-preliminaries-resume-2024-03-19/</link><description>卡塔尔将于周四对阵科威特，恢复首次世界杯预选赛的资格，教练席稳定，但在本土卫冕亚洲杯六周后，球场上的情况发生了变化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:58:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-champions-qatar-shift-focus-world-cup-preliminaries-resume-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>行业高管表示，太阳能电池板价格将在两年内保持低位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/solar-panel-prices-remain-low-up-two-years-says-industry-exec-2024-03-19/</link><description>马来西亚一位行业高管周二表示，太阳能电池板的价格在过去 12 个月内几乎减半，并将在两年内保持在当前水平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/solar-panel-prices-remain-low-up-two-years-says-industry-exec-2024-03-19/</guid></item><item><title>智能手机销量强劲，小米营收增长 11%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-xiaomi-q4-2023-revenue-rises-11-beats-estimates-2024-03-19/</link><description>中国小米公布第四季度收入增长 10.9%，由于智能手机销售强劲，该行业显示出复苏迹象，调整后净利润超出预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 09:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-xiaomi-q4-2023-revenue-rises-11-beats-estimates-2024-03-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>